<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Email - SyncSplit</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        font-family:
          -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica,
          Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 40px 20px;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #000000;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .otp-container {
        margin: 40px 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-family:
          ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        color: #000000;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .expiry {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888888;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
      .divider {
        margin: 40px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888888;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .footer p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #888888;
        margin: 4px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">SyncSplit</div>

      <h1>Verification code</h1>

      <p>Hello <%= username %>,</p>
      <p>
        To complete your registration and secure your
        <strong>SyncSplit</strong> account, please use the following
        verification code:
      </p>

      <div class="otp-container">
        <div class="otp-code"><%= activationCode %></div>
        <div class="expiry">Expires in 10 minutes</div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #888888">
        If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.
      </p>

      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>SyncSplit Protocol — Precision Financial Tracking</p>
        <p>© 2026 All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
